        "paragraph_index": 0,
        "text": "SRD‑46 lists **6 distinct linked reference records** for reported **log K** measurements of the **Cd²⁺–chloride** system. Within the retrieved Cd–Cl dataset, these cover the aqueous complexes **CdCl⁺, CdCl₂(aq), and CdCl₃⁻**; I did **not** find an ML4 entry in the resolved catalog for this system.\n\n| Item | Result |\n|---|---:|\n| Metal | Cd²⁺ (`metal_26`) |\n| Ligand | chloride (`ligand_10163`) |\n| Total Cd–Cl entries in catalog | 30 |\n| log K measurement rows | 18 |\n| Ancillary thermodynamic rows (ΔH/ΔS) | 12 |\n| Distinct linked reference records for log K rows | 6 |\n| Temperature range in retrieved stability rows | 25 °C only |\n| Ionic-strength range | 0–4 M |",
